704026f.text:
Downing Street, west side, at Guincy Street. the 4-story building is Nos. 6-8 Downing Street; its right hand portion and the vacant lots adioining it, correspond to the course of the Clove Road, which was also known as "the old road to Bedford". The frame houses in the background, front on
Grand Ave.
About 191O.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
